Hi Beth,

Is that 78 Bus running with the original fuel injection?

Sounds like the Cold-Start injector or Themal Time Switch may be 
malfunctioning. There's an FI manual online at...

http://www.everybus.com/~greg_potts/Bosch_L-Jetronic_FI_Manual/

...that will help with troubleshooting.

Happy trails,

